## Steps to install RStudio in Linux (Ubuntu 22) version ##

# install R #
sudo apt-get install r-base

sudo apt-get install gdebi-core # GDebi = installer to install deb files on Linux-Debian distributions

wget https://download2.rstudio.org/server/jammy/amd64/rstudio-server-2024.09.1-394-amd64.deb ## we can also download the deb files from the following link: https://posit.co/download/rstudio-desktop/

sudo gdebi rstudio-server-2024.09.1-394-amd64.deb
